                  The left half of the hyperbola is drawn with a dashed line, while the right half of the parabola is drawn with a solid line.
                </p>
              </description>
              <latex-image>

              \begin{tikzpicture}

              \begin{axis}[
              ymin=-1100,ymax=1100,
